description:
Night Ranger
High Road (Deluxe Edition) (2014)





allmusic.com...

The Bay Area-based hard rock legends' first collection of new material since 2011's well-received Somewhere in California, 2014's High Road, released to coincide with the group's 30th anniversary, features 11 brand new songs that, according to bass player/frontman Jack Blades, are built on a foundation of "classic Night Ranger feel-good, high-energy kick-ass rock 'n' roll." Produced by the band and, like Somewhere in California and 2008's Hole in the Sun, released via Frontiers Records, Night Ranger's 11th studio long-player is sure to please both longtime fans and entice new listeners with its winning mix of pop craftsmanship and hard rock backbone. [A Deluxe CD/DVD added bonus videos and a "making-of" DVD.]
